import "../styles/Registration.css" import { useState } from "react"; const Registration = () => { const [regData, setRegData] = useState({ email: '', password: '', password_verify: '', name_organization: '', site_url: '', phone_1: '', phone_2: '', about: '', FIO: '', city: '' }) const [isOrganization, setIsOrganization] = useState(false); async function registration(e) { e.preventDefault() const email = regData.email const password = regData.password const password_verify = regData.password_verify const name_organization = regData.name_organization const site_url = regData.site_url const phone_1 = regData.phone_1 const phone_2 = regData.phone_2 const about = regData.about const FIO = regData.FIO const city = regData.city if (isOrganization) { const id_type_organization = 2 } else { const id_type_organization = 1 } setRegData({ email: '', password: '', password_verify: '', name_organization: '', site_url: '', phone_1: '', phone_2: '', about: '', FIO: '', city: '' }) } return (
setRegData({...regData, email: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, password: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, password_verify: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, site_url: e.target.value})} />
{isOrganization ?
setRegData({...regData, name_organization: e.target.value})} />
:
setRegData({...regData, FIO: e.target.value})} />
}
setRegData({...regData, phone_1: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, phone_2: e.target.value})} />
setIsOrganization(!isOrganization)} />
); }; export default Registration
